# {{ bakery.project_name }} — frontend (Next.js 16 skeleton)

> Minimal Next.js 16 + React 19 + TypeScript 6 App Router skeleton. No auth, no UI library — bring your own.
>
> What's wired for you: Next.js same-origin rewrites to Django, OWASP-conscious security headers, the Compose service, and the workspace.

## Run it

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm dev                          # next on http://localhost:{{ bakery.frontend_dev_port }}
docker compose -f compose.local.yml up
```

